<!-- A Look C | Revamped Version 1 [Custom Colors] || Made by ACP (acodingperson) @Toyhou.se

    HANDY WEBSITES:
        > Font Awesome v5 (for old icons): https://fontawesome.com/
        > Font Awesome v6 (for new icons): https://fontawesome.com/v6.0/icons
        > W3 Schools Bootstrap: https://www.w3schools.com/bootstrap/
        > W3 Schools HTML: https://www.w3schools.com/html/default.asp
        > Bootstrap Docs: https://getbootstrap.com/docs/5.1/getting-started/introduction/

    COLORS USED:
        (note: "color" determines color of text)
        > Main Color of Text: #000 (check "container")

        > Container:
            - border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125)
            - color: #000 <-- determines main color of text

        > In Quote:
            - border-color: #8f8f8f
            - background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7)
            - color: #222222
            
        > In Content Block:
            - background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7)
            - border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)

        > In Right Column:
            - background-color: #fff
            - adjectives block:
                ~ color: #fff
                ~ background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5)
            - meta info list:
                ~ main background-color: #eeeeee
                ~ background-color of theme song btn: #e3e3e3
            
        > In Left Column:
            - background-color: #fff
            - name block:
                ~ background-color: #c7c7c7
            - navigation:
                ~ background-color of nav pills: #aaaaaa
                ~ color of icons: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)
            - in appearance block:
                ~ info box background-color: #eeeeee
            - in personality block:
                ~ info box background-color: #eeeeee
            - in ability block:
                ~ stat box background-color: #eeeeee
                ~ progress background-color: #dadada
                ~ progress bar background-color: #000
            - in history block:
                ~ subheader muted text color: #797979
            - in trivia block:
                ~ credit text color: #e9e9e9 | credit hr background-color: #c9c9c9
            - in links block:
                ~ relationship names color: #000
                ~ relationship type color: #5a5a5a
            - in credit block:
                ~ icon colors: #000

    TO KEEP IN MIND:
        > replace all placeholder images (those that begin with https://via.placeholder.com/) with the images of your choosing
        > read through and understand my TOS - https://toyhou.se/~bulletins/491483.global-tos
        > bump my thread~ - https://toyhou.se/~forums/16.htmlcss-graphics/245374.the-codes-of-a-person-acp-s-coding-thread
        > you can erase this entire block for ease of use

    THANK YOU FOR USING <3

-->







